'''ROM Location:''' Bank 01, approximately $9500-$953c (60 bytes = 30 levels × 2 bytes)

===Experience Gain===

Experience is gained directly from defeated monsters with no bonuses or modifiers:

<pre>
EXP Gained = Monster's Base EXP
</pre>

* No level scaling
* No equipment bonuses
* No party bonuses (single player game)
* Fixed values from monster stats table

'''ROM Location:''' Bank 03, approximately $c700 (BattleVictory routine)

==HP Growth System==

===HP Gain Per Level===

HP growth uses a lookup table with random variance.

'''Formula:'''
<pre>
Base HP Gain = HPGainTable[New Level]
Random Bonus = Random(0, 3)
Final HP Gain = Base HP Gain + Random Bonus
New Max HP = Old Max HP + Final HP Gain
