==Stat Growth System==

===Strength (STR) Growth===

STR growth is randomized and depends on whether the level is even or odd.

'''Formula:'''
<pre>
If (New Level is Even):
    STR Gain = Random(2, 4)
Else:  (New Level is Odd)
    STR Gain = Random(1, 3)

New STR = Old STR + STR Gain
</pre>

'''Average Growth:'''
* Even levels: ~3 STR
* Odd levels: ~2 STR
* Level 1-30: ~75 total STR gain

'''Constants:'''
* EVEN_LEVEL_STR_MIN = 2
* EVEN_LEVEL_STR_MAX = 4
* ODD_LEVEL_STR_MIN = 1
* ODD_LEVEL_STR_MAX = 3

'''ROM Location:''' Bank 03, approximately $cc00 (LevelUpSTR routine)

===Agility (AGI) Growth===

AGI growth is inverse to STR - odd levels get better gains.

'''Formula:'''
<pre>
If (New Level is Odd):
    AGI Gain = Random(2, 5)
Else:  (New Level is Even)
    AGI Gain = Random(1, 3)

New AGI = Old AGI + AGI Gain
</pre>

'''Average Growth:'''
* Odd levels: ~3.5 AGI
* Even levels: ~2 AGI
* Level 1-30: ~85 total AGI gain

'''Constants:'''
* ODD_LEVEL_AGI_MIN = 2
* ODD_LEVEL_AGI_MAX = 5
* EVEN_LEVEL_AGI_MIN = 1
* EVEN_LEVEL_AGI_MAX = 3

'''ROM Location:''' Bank 03, approximately $cc50 (LevelUpAGI routine)

