==Level-Up Procedure==

===Technical Flow===

When player gains enough EXP for level-up:

1. Check current EXP against level requirements table
2. If threshold met, increment level
3. Calculate HP gain (base + random)
4. Calculate MP gain (base + random)
5. Calculate STR gain (even/odd formula + random)
6. Calculate AGI gain (odd/even formula + random)
7. Check spell learning table for new spells
8. Recalculate ATK/DEF (base stats + equipment)
9. Display level-up message and stat gains
10. If multiple level-ups, repeat

'''ROM Location:''' Bank 03, approximately $ca00 (ProcessLevelUp routine)

===Stat Recalculation===

After level-up, attack and defense are recalculated:

<pre>
Player ATK = Base STR + Weapon Bonus + Fighter's Ring (if equipped)
Player DEF = Base Defense + Armor Bonus + Shield Bonus
</pre>

Equipment bonuses are fixed values from equipment tables.

