==Modification Examples==

===Fast Level Progression===

Edit EXP requirements table in Bank 01 ~$9500:

<pre>
; Original:
ExpRequirements:
    .word $0000  ; Level 1
    .word $0007  ; Level 2: 7 EXP
    .word $0017  ; Level 3: 23 EXP

; Modified (fast):
ExpRequirements:
    .word $0000  ; Level 1
    .word $0001  ; Level 2: 1 EXP
    .word $0002  ; Level 3: 2 EXP
</pre>

===Guaranteed Max Stat Gains===

Edit random ranges in stat growth routines:

<pre>
; Original STR gain (even levels):
LDA #2          ; Min gain
STA TempMin
LDA #4          ; Max gain
STA TempMax
JSR Random

; Modified (always max):
LDA #4          ; Always gain 4
</pre>

